ve; 19h30, dans les locaux de HEM Rabat, sur &laquo; La place du Maroc dans un nouvel ordre Atlantique &raquo;. Cette manifestation intervient ainsi dans le prolongement du dossier Economia pr&eacute;sentant une s&eacute;rie de travaux de recherche relatifs au lien entre le Maroc et le bassin Atlantique.<\/p>\r\n<p>More information on the event: <a href=\"http:\/\/hem.ac.ma\/fr\/evenements-recherche\/table-ronde-economia-quelle-place-maroc-nouvel-ordre-atlantique\">http:\/\/hem.ac.ma\/fr\/evenements-recherche\/table-ronde-economia-quelle-place-maroc-nouvel-ordre-atlantique<\/a> &nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p><strong>The program may be downloaded here:<\/strong><\/p>","views":"133","shares":"0","tweets":"0","mails":"0","published":true,"image":true,"featured":false,"type":"1","created":"2015-10-23 19:30:00","modified":"2016-01-29 04:18:08"},"User":{"id":"1","email":"info@onebigrobot.com","first_name":"Administrator","last_name":null,"password":"c8d482e69d7de06cc7429d3b9484c8145fdfb818","code":"","role":"0","type":"0","published":true,"created":"2014-06-26 10:44:32","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Event":{"id":"1118","datetime":"2015-10-23 17:30:00","country":"Morocco","city":"Rabat","address":"","map":""},"Resource":[{"id":"170","content_id":"1118","type":"1","file_name":"1118-Table ronde Economia.pdf","description":"Table ronde Economia","created":"2015-10-02 11:19:56","modified":"2015-10-02 11:19:56"}],"ContentTag":[{"id":"6795","content_id":"1118","tag_id":"44","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"44","code":"the-atlantic1","name":"The Atlantic","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"0068AD","created":"2013-10-30 14:16:17","modified":"2013-08-02 12:27:19"}},{"id":"6793","content_id":"1118","tag_id":"36","order":"1","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"36","code":"events","name":"Events","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"995B31","created":"2013-09-27 09:58:37","modified":"2013-09-