 institutions","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"EBC635","created":"2013-10-21 17:29:28","modified":"2013-09-27 10:04:26"}},{"id":"1653","content_id":"35","tag_id":"54","order":"10","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"54","code":"perspectives","name":"Perspectives","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"FFFFFF","created":"2013-09-27 10:43:59","modified":"2013-09-27 10:43:59"}},{"id":"1654","content_id":"35","tag_id":"24","order":"11","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"24","code":"political-relations","name":"Political relations","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"FFFFFF","created":"2013-09-27 10:04:54","modified":"2013-09-27 10:04:54"}},{"id":"1655","content_id":"35","tag_id":"26","order":"12","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"26","code":"resources-and-environment","name":"Resources and environment","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"9AC4AB","created":"2013-10-21 17:29:28","modified":"2013-09-27 10:08:22"}},{"id":"1656","content_id":"35","tag_id":"21","order":"13","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"21","code":"security","name":"Security","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"C31F4A","created":"2013-10-21 17:29:28","modified":"2013-09-27 10:08:37"}},{"id":"1657","content_id":"35","tag_id":"147","order":"14","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"147","code":"international-relations","name":"international relations","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"#FFFFFF","created":"2013-11-18 11:32:59","modified":"2013-11-18 11:32:59"}},{"id":"1658","content_id":"35","tag_id":"129","order":"15","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"129","code":"pacific-area","name":"Pacific area","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"FFFFFF","created":"2013-10-10 11:59:17","modified":"2013-10-10 11:59:17"}}],"MainCategory":{"ContentTag":{"id":"1659","content_id":"35","tag_id":"44","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Tag":{"id":"44","code":"the-atlantic1","name":"The Atlantic","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"0068AD","created":"2013-10-30 14:16:17","modified":"2013-08-02 12:27:19"}},"Format":[]},{"Content":{"id":"34","code":"published-cidob-on-the-atlantic-space","user_id":"1","title":"Published! CIDOB on the Atlantic space","abstract":"A new issue of CIDOB Journal of Afers Internacionals has been recently published. Under the title &ldquo;Rediscovering the Atlantic space&rdquo;, the issue (in Spanish) sheds light on the processes taking place in the Atlantic space, not very explored yet.","body":"<p>The Atlantic Basin is becoming a central scenario for globalization and, as such, it deserves the same attention as the emerging Pacific area. Within the Atlantic space, there are growing links in the fields of energy, commerce, human security, norms, values and other issues related to the ocean itself. As interdependency relations grow through this basin, new opportunities emerge, but also new vulnerabilities affect its interlinking societies. With more and more urgent common problems, Atlantic states and regions are seeking with renewed interest their counterparts in all shores of the ocean. Authors from different shores of the Atlantic, some of them partners of ATLANTIC FUTURE or members of our Scientific and Advisory Panel, analyse from a wide range of theoretical and empirical orientations the consequences of the current changes and transformations within the Atlantic space.<\/p>\r\n<p>Check the contents <a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/publication_series\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/rediscovering_the_atlantic_space\" target=\"_blank\">here.<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/introduction_a_new_perspective_on_the_atlantic\">Introduction: a new perspective on the Atlantic<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p>Anna Ayuso and Elina Viilup<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/atlantic_communities_asymmetries_and_convergences\">Atlantic communities: asymmetries and convergences<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Dorval Brunelle<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/towards_a_governance_agenda_for_the_emerging_atlantic_hemisphere\">Towards a governance agenda for the emerging Atlantic Hemisphere<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Daniel S. Hamilton<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/atlantic_energy_and_the_strategic_outlook\">Atlantic energy and the strategic outlook<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Paul Isbell<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/trade_in_the_atlantic_basin_2000_2012_a_panoramic_view\">Trade in the Atlantic Basin, 2000-2012: a panoramic view<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Lorena Ruano<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/south_south_cooperation_a_key_element_in_the_emergence_of_the_south_atlantic\">South-South cooperation: a key element in the emergence of the South Atlantic<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Christian Freres<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/competitive_integration_models_in_the_western_hemisphere_competitive_leadership_or_mutual_denial\">Competitive integration models in the Western hemisphere: competitive leadership or mutual denial?<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Cintia Quiliconi<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/china_s_growing_role_in_the_south_atlantic\">China&rsquo;s growing role in the South Atlantic<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Adriana Erthal Abdenur and Danilo Marcondes de Souza Neto<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/security_dynamics_in_the_south_atlantic_brazil_and_the_united_states_in_africa\">Security dynamics in the South Atlantic: Brazil and the United States in Africa<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Pedro Seabra<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cidob.org\/en\/publications\/articulos\/revista_cidob_d_afers_internacionals\/102_103\/obama_s_european_policy_and_the_transatlantic_relations\">Obama&rsquo;s European policy and the transatlantic relations<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>Juan Tovar Ruiz<\/p>","views":"423","shares":"0","tweets":"1","mails":"0","published":true,"image":true,"featured":true,"type":"0","created":"2013-10-10 11:52:00","modified":"2016-01-15 16:55:17"},"User":{"id":"1","email":"info@onebigrobot.com","first_name":"Administrator","last_name":null,"password":"c8d482e69d7de06cc7429d3b9484c8145fdfb818","code":"","role":"0","type":"0","published":true,"created":"2014-06-26 10:44:32","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Event":{"id":null,"datetime":null,"country":null,"city":null,"address":null,"map":null},"Resource":[],"ContentTag":[{"id":"5424","content_id":"34","tag_id":"44","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"44","code":"the-atlantic1","name":"The Atlantic","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"0068AD","created":"2013-10-30 14:16:17","modified":"2013-08-02 12:27:19"}},{"id":"5405","content_id":"34","tag_id":"5","order":"1","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"5","code":"atlantic-space","name":"Atlantic space","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"FFFFFF","created":"2013-09-27 09:55:08","modified":"2013-09-27 09:55:08"}},{"id":"5406","content_id":"34","tag_id":"1","order":"2","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"1","code":"atlantic-basin","name":"A