r or thinner than others. Contrary to Friedman&rsquo;s notion that &ldquo;the world is flat&rdquo;, the world may not be becoming flatter but lumpier, with power and dependencies changing and flowing in different ways. This is why the exploration of the new Atlantic space is so relevant and important. ATLANTIC FUTURE will explore precisely where the world is not even, and how globalistion is changing the very contours of power and interdependence among the EU and its major Atlantic partners.<\/p>","views":"156","shares":"0","tweets":"0","mails":"0","published":true,"image":true,"featured":true,"type":"0","created":"2013-07-19 10:10:00","modified":"2016-02-01 20:07:33"},"User":{"id":"1","email":"info@onebigrobot.com","first_name":"Administrator","last_name":null,"password":"c8d482e69d7de06cc7429d3b9484c8145fdfb818","code":"","role":"0","type":"0","published":true,"created":"2014-06-26 10:44:32","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Event":{"id":null,"datetime":null,"country":null,"city":null,"address":null,"map":null},"Resource":[],"ContentTag":[{"id":"1446","content_id":"2","tag_id":"44","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"44","code":"the-atlantic1","name":"The Atlantic","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"0068AD","created":"2013-10-30 14:16:17","modified":"2013-08-02 12:27:19"}},{"id":"1440","content_id":"2","tag_id":"6","order":"1","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"6","code":"globalisation","name":"Globalisation","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"FFFFFF","created":"2013-09-27 10:03:52","modified":"2013-09-27 10:03:52"}},{"id":"1441","content_id":"2","tag_id":"121","order":"2","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"121","code":"interdependence","name":"Interdependence","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"FFFFFF","created":"2013-09-27 13:12:07","modified":"2013-09-27 13:12:07"}},{"id":"1442","content_id":"2","tag_id":"5","order