epresentatives of local institutions and members of academia. He referred to the ATLANTIC FUTURE as an ambitious project that has the potential of bringing to the fore new ideas and new perspectives. To think in transatlantic terms is, according to Professor Brunelle, &ldquo;a good way of tackling old problems from a new angle&rdquo;.<\/p>\r\n<p>Read the full report.<\/p>","views":"166","shares":"0","tweets":"0","mails":"0","published":true,"image":true,"featured":true,"type":"0","created":"2013-06-24 10:18:00","modified":"2016-02-07 16:36:16"},"User":{"id":"1","email":"info@onebigrobot.com","first_name":"Administrator","last_name":null,"password":"c8d482e69d7de06cc7429d3b9484c8145fdfb818","code":"","role":"0","type":"0","published":true,"created":"2014-06-26 10:44:32","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Event":{"id":null,"datetime":null,"country":null,"city":null,"address":null,"map":null},"Resource":[{"id":"6","content_id":"24","type":"1","file_name":"24-Rethinking the Atlantic_Report.pdf","description":"","created":"2013-07-29 12:29:32","modified":"2013-07-29 12:29:32"}],"ContentTag":[{"id":"2234","content_id":"24","tag_id":"25","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"25","code":"people-and-institutions","name":"People and institutions","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"EBC635","created":"2013-10-21 17:29:28","modified":"2013-09-27 10:04:26"}},{"id":"2229","content_id":"24","tag_id":"38","order":"1","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"38","code":"atlantic-community","name":"Atlantic community","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"FFFFFF","created":"2013-09-27 13:12:17","modified":"2013-09-27 13:12:17"}},{"id":"2230","content_id":"24","tag_id":"54","order":"2","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"54","code":"perspectives","name":"Perspectives","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"FFFFFF","created":"2013-09-27 10:43:59","modified"