esentations, and discussions to mark the fifth anniversary of Ecologic Institute in Washington, DC (EIUS).<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=0gEdsqyM_Z4&amp;feature=youtu.be\">&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>","views":"71","shares":"0","tweets":"0","mails":"0","published":true,"image":true,"featured":true,"type":"1","created":"2013-04-03 12:00:00","modified":"2016-01-13 12:39:09"},"User":{"id":"1","email":"info@onebigrobot.com","first_name":"Administrator","last_name":null,"password":"c8d482e69d7de06cc7429d3b9484c8145fdfb818","code":"","role":"0","type":"0","published":true,"created":"2014-06-26 10:44:32","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Event":{"id":"31","datetime":"2013-04-24 09:00:00","country":"United States","city":"Washington","address":"","map":""},"Resource":[],"ContentTag":[{"id":"2223","content_id":"31","tag_id":"26","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"26","code":"resources-and-environment","name":"Resources and environment","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"9AC4AB","created":"2013-10-21 17:29:28","modified":"2013-09-27 10:08:22"}},{"id":"2222","content_id":"31","tag_id":"36","order":"1","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"36","code":"events","name":"Events","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"995B31","created":"2013-09-27 09:58:37","modified":"2013-09-27 09:58:37"}}],"MainCategory":{"ContentTag":{"id":"2223","content_id":"31","tag_id":"26","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Tag":{"id":"26","code":"resources-and-environment","name":"Resources and environment","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"9AC4AB","created":"2013-10-21 17:29:28","modified":"2013-09-27 10:08:22"}},"Format":[]},{"Content":{"id":"27","code":"event-kick-off-meeting","user_id":"1","title":"Event: Kick-off meeting","abstract":"The kick-off meeting of the ATLANTIC FUTURE was held at CIDOB in Barcelona on 22 March 2013.","body":"<p>The kick-off meeting of the ATLANTIC FUTURE was held at CIDOB in Barcelona on 22 March 2013. The project coordinator, CIDOB, gave an overview of the Project and the timing of the different phases and the participating partners discussed the main lines of research in a closed meeting.<\/p>","views":"103","shares":"0","tweets":"0","mails":"0","published":true,"image":true,"featured":false,"type":"0","created":"2013-04-03 09:00:00","modified":"2016-02-08 12:24:22"},"User":{"id":"1","email":"info@onebigrobot.com","first_name":"Administrator","last_name":null,"password":"c8d482e69d7de06cc7429d3b9484c8145fdfb818","code":"","role":"0","type":"0","published":true,"created":"2014-06-26 10:44:32","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Event":{"id":null,"datetime":null,"country":null,"city":null,"address":null,"map":null},"Resource":[],"ContentTag":[{"id":"2213","content_id":"27","tag_id":"44","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"44","code":"the-atlantic1","name":"The Atlantic","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"0068AD","created":"2013-10-30 14:16:17","modified":"2013-08-02 12:27:19"}},{"id":"2211","content_id":"27","tag_id":"36","order":"1","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"36","code":"events","name":"Events","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"995B31","created":"2013-09-27 09:58:37","modified":"2013-09-27 09:58:37"}},{"id":"2212","content_id":"27","tag_id":"46","order":"2","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","Tag":{"id":"46","code":"barcelona-centre-for-international-affairs-cidob","name":"Barcelona Centre for International Affairs (CIDOB)","type":"0","mandatory":false,"color":"#FFFFFF","created":"2013-12-02 14:29:22","modified":"2013-12-02 14:29:22"}}],"MainCategory":{"ContentTag":{"id":"2213","content_id":"27","tag_id":"44","order":"0","created":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Tag":{"id":"44","code":"the-atlantic1","name":"The Atlantic","type":"1","mandatory":true,"color":"0068AD","created":"2013-10-30 14:16:17","modified":"2013-08-02 12:27:19"}},"Format":[]},{"Content":{"id":"6","code":"what-will-atlantic-future-deliver-","user_id":"1","title":"What will ATLANTIC FUTURE deliver? ","abstract":"The ATLANTIC FUTURE project will deliver a wide range of deliverables throughout the 3 years of research.","body":"<p>ATLANTIC FUTURE aims at reaching different audiences through its deliverables, be it the scientific community, policy makers, the business community, the media and civil society, or the general public. The main deliverables are adapted to the targeted audiences and will be the following:<\/p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">A <strong>Monograph<\/strong> that will provide the answer to the research question on whether an Atlantic Area is emerging and will lay out emerging trends and possible scenarios in the wider Atlantic space.<\/li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Datasets <\/strong>containing large amounts of data on each of the four thematic areas of the Project: Economy and finance, Security, People and institutions and Resources and environment. This collection of data aims to identify the main drivers for and obstacles to cooperation in the Atlantic space across the four areas.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">An interactive <strong>Atlas of the Atlantic<\/strong> that will map the changes in the Atlantic and that will be a novel and unique visual image of globalization in the Atlantic and the four continents bordering it. The Atlas of the Atlantic will be a useful instrument for scientific researchers, students, policy-makers, journalists and a wider audience.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Working papers <\/strong>and <strong>Scientific papers<\/strong> that will contribute to the research on the Atlantic and will tackle different issues. Among others, but not limited to, the papers will be on the Atlantic space, on thematic areas such as energy, economy, security, political and social relations, on regionalism and interregionalism, on regional perspectives, and on future scenarios.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Policy papers<\/strong>, focusing on policy analysis and providing policy recommendations for the EU.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Policy and business <strong>briefs<\/strong> that will distil some of the Project results, directed to the policy-making and the business community audiences.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>ATLANTIC 500<\/strong>, a virtual community that will bring together 500 mid-level stakeholders in the Atlantic. The objective of Atlantic 500 is to map tendencies, build scenarios in global governance and make them easily understandable and readily available only. Atlantic 500 will in the future link a global community and will offer useful prospective insights into the future of global governance and the role of transatlantic partners and other global powers.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Audiovisual instruments<\/strong> in the form of short pieces of animation that will feature some of the highlights of ATLANTIC FUTURE and that will disseminate the results of the Project to a wider audience.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>","views":"166","shares":"1","tweets":"0","mails":"0","published":true,"image":true,"featured":true,"type":"0","created":"2013-03-16 16:33:00","modified":"2016-02-04 18:15:38"},"User":{"id":"1","email":"info@onebigrobot.com","first_name":"Administrator","last_name":null,"password":"c8d482e69d7de06cc7429d3b9484c8145fdfb818","code":"","role":"0","type":"0","published":true,"created":"2014-06-26 10:44:32","modified":"0000-00-00 00:00:00"},"Event":{"id":null,"datetime":null,"country":null,"city":null,"address":null,"map":null},"Resource":[],"ContentTag":[{"